    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "It would be the first time using `process.env.NODE_ENV` in our source code, meaning it's used only when running `yarn dev` for our contributors. IMO it would include too much potential complexity at a time where we are already overloaded.\r\n\r\nWaiting to include this in the actual user bundle would provide much more value. What do you think?",
